l greaves.  This got my strength over 110 and my stamina over 100.  The rest of the crustacean shell armor really helped and now I have 128 strength and 135 stamina.  Also, invest in some Iksar Scaled Gloves for 50-100pp (10ac, 3str, 3sta, 10hp, or close to that), or if you can afford more expensive, gaunts of the black (15ac, 3wis, 5str) which I bought for 350pp.  What are really killing me right now are my non-visible slots.  I have a bronze girdle in waist, a banded cloak in back, and a chipped bone collar in neck.  These are really hurting my AC and stats.  I've been thinking of getting spiderfur collar/cloak, and an FBSS.  but that's about 5k on Bertoxx.  won't be getting that any time soon, so a more realistic goal for me right now is ry'gorr for neck and back, and a spiderfur waist for around 1.5k. <br><br>Avethar Soulforge, officer of &lt;Winds of Time&gt;<br>33 High Elf Paladin<br>Bertoxxulous server <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showPrevMessage?topicID=374.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showNextMessage?topicID=374.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=374.topic&index=2><img src=http://eq1.castersrealm.com/pon/images/reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.emailToFriend?topicID=374.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.threadControl?topicID=374.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (